<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Rule: stratum_interconnect_module_planar_position_constraint
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Layered_interconnect_module_2d_design_mim.stratum_interconnect_module_planar_position_constraint">
The <b>stratum_interconnect_module_planar_position_constraint</b> rule constrains the
<express_ref 
linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.mapped_item.mapping_target"/>, <express_ref 
linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.mapped_item.mapping_source"/> and use of a <express_ref 
linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.mapped_item"/> when it is a
planar positioned stratum shape in interconnect module.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Layered_interconnect_module_2d_design_mim.stratum_interconnect_module_planar_position_constraint.wr:WR1">
Each <express_ref 
linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.mapped_item"/> that has a name = 'planar positioned stratum shape in 
interconnect module' shall have a <express_ref 
linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.mapped_item.mapping_target"/> that is an <express_ref linkend="geometry_schema:ir_express:geometry_schema.axis2_placement_2d"/>.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Rule: stratum_planar_shape_constraint
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Layered_interconnect_module_2d_design_mim.stratum_planar_shape_constraint">
The <b>stratum_planar_shape_constraint</b> rule requires each <express_ref 
linkend="product_property_representation_schema:ir_express:product_property_representation_schema.shape_representation"/>
to be related to an <express_ref linkend="geometry_schema:ir_express:geometry_schema.axis2_placement_2d"/> and a <express_ref 
linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.product_definition_shape"/>
when it is implementing the arm concept
of <express_ref linkend="Layered_interconnect_module_2d_design:arm:Layered_interconnect_module_2d_design_arm.Stratum_planar_shape"/>.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Layered_interconnect_module_2d_design_mim.stratum_planar_shape_constraint.wr:WR1">
Each <express_ref 
linkend="product_property_representation_schema:ir_express:product_property_representation_schema.shape_representation"/> that [has a name = 'planar projected shape']
[is related to a stratum through a <express_ref 
linkend="product_property_representation_schema:ir_express:product_property_representation_schema.property_definition_representation"/>] shall
have at least one items satisfied by an <express_ref linkend="geometry_schema:ir_express:geometry_schema.axis2_placement_2d"/>.
</ext_description>

